{"tid":1547644,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"分享一下咁多日既免費搭港鐵心得","createTime":"2019-09-06T17:30:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T15:40:53.000Z","uid":302348,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a25373a9fe82ac56a9ef4cd7863e04d9289bfe37","tid":1547644,"uid":302348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:30:42.000Z","msg":"分享比一眾唔夠膽跳閘既人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我個人認為新閘好過舊閘。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新閘你只要一邊跟住前面既人出，一邊再扮拍卡，係會有短暫既響聲，但係你只要戴住耳機，淡定少少就得，係人流多既站好難捉邊個冇拍卡。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />第二個方法你撞閘，踢一邊門就得，但係會有少少明顯，唔建議細膽既人做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />第三係跳閘，難度最高，但唔建議細膽既人做，同埋比較細粒既人冇咁有著數。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以總結黎講：跟前人&gt;&gt;踢&gt;跳。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n舊閘比較麻煩少少。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />事關港鐵好似做緊加固工程，部分站得，部分站唔得，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有部分站好容易出（部就唔講啦，唔想佢地前後再加固），不過今日試過葵興站，太實啦，最後我跳過去算。舊閘有樣好處就係唔會有響聲，大家細膽既人可以試下舊閘出，如果冇黃衫粉紅衫既人你點玩都得，推又得，跳又得，甚至係下面捐過去都得。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最後都係入閘前扮一扮拍卡啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依排除左搭巴士之外，搭<strong><em><ins>港鐵係免費架</ins></em></strong>！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f66a6c71f0c2bfcb489396880410ddfc2c6670c","tid":1547644,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:36:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一句講晒，睇哩個post</span></span><br />\n[置頂/請廣傳/多圖] 907 遊客LOOK 暢遊大嶼山指南<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1547426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1547426</a>"},{"pid":"536bcf5a96550f710833670b519ebca4f84df9b3","tid":1547644,"uid":83081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:38:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e973bd956d7be52ae336712139c4da9a8bdc8fa4","tid":1547644,"uid":124811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:42:59.000Z","msg":"聽日要繼續呀！<br />\n推"},{"pid":"c67f353c408ffe65cc8ec26c6160346a60b64642","tid":1547644,"uid":310534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:45:26.000Z","msg":"支持免費搭狗鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2227df882e9552b22be8fc1117fd3d0b5fc521db","tid":1547644,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:51:04.000Z","msg":"mk站果種新型雙門一跳會好響<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70da28cc19ceeab86cc2d50884a6870ad1a45bbc","tid":1547644,"uid":302348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2227df882e9552b22be8fc1117fd3d0b5fc521db","tid":1547644,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:51:04.000Z","msg":"mk站果種新型雙門一跳會好響<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:56:07.000Z","msg":"係呀 會響架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以跟人行最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e86eaa87432d49146902016a61125c00b3f11bd","tid":1547644,"uid":275884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:40:53.000Z","msg":"香港人！我哋需要改變生活習慣救香港呀！<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dKJOcT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dKJOcT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}